							<p>Perhaps you want to know more about me and my work, or perhaps you have a suggestion for improvement. Please share your contact information with me.</p>
							<p>Good communication takes time. I prioritize in person interactions with people I care about and for causes I believe are worthwhile. My time to reply might be lighting fast or a couple weeks, but I will always try to respond. I will strive to be explicit as to what time I can reasonably devote to develop a relationship over asynchronous communication channels. Take care and continue working hard on your personal projects!</p>
